PMCID: PMC7656098
PMID: 33199940


746. Clin Infect Dis. 2021 Oct 5;73(7):e2077-e2085. doi: 10.1093/cid/ciaa1698.

Cost-effectiveness of a Novel Lipoarabinomannan Test for Tuberculosis in 
Patients With Human Immunodeficiency Virus.

Reddy KP(1)(2)(3), Denkinger CM(4), Broger T(4), McCann NC(1), Gupta-Wright 
A(5)(6)(7), Kerkhoff AD(8), Pei PP(1), Shebl FM(1)(3), Fielding KL(9)(10), Nicol 
